{"tid":2359873,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】中國石家莊 354 人檢測陽性 當地交通停駛 全市居家隔離 7 日","createTime":"2021-01-09T08:49:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-10T06:48:38.000Z","uid":48083,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d223fdc4a7fb59cdb14e0fb68de87149d6933ae2","tid":2359873,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T08:49:58.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫情全球肆虐，一度聲稱國內疫情受控的中國，疫情最近急劇反彈。石家莊市早前錄得多宗確診個案，河北省今日（9日）疫情新聞發佈會公布，當局檢測全市逾 1000 萬人，累計共 354 人檢測呈陽性，其中藁城區佔 298 人。當地宣布石家莊「封城」，鐵路、機場、巴士、的士等公共交通工具全面停止運作，未有公布恢復時間。當局亦宣布，石家莊市及邢台市昨日起「居家 7 日」，不可出社區及村莊，以防止疫情擴散。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/china/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%9F%B3%E5%AE%B6%E8%8E%8A-354-%E4%BA%BA%E6%AA%A2%E6%B8%AC%E9%99%BD%E6%80%A7-%E7%95%B6%E5%9C%B0%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E5%81%9C%E9%A7%9B-%E5%85%A8%E5%B8%82%E5%B1%85%E5%AE%B6-7-%E6%97%A5/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%259F%25B3%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%258E%258A-354-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E6%25B8%25AC%25E9%2599%25BD%25E6%2580%25A7-%25E7%2595%25B6%25E5%259C%25B0%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E9%2580%259A%25E5%2581%259C%25E9%25A7%259B-%25E5%2585%25A8%25E5%25B8%2582%25E5%25B1%2585%25E5%25AE%25B6-7-%25E6%2597%25A5%2F&d=M%2BQ4vsyFJ%2Bls%2BsYkNkBEXUn12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=5c7fe98a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%259F%25B3%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%258E%258A-354-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E6%25B8%25AC%25E9%2599%25BD%25E6%2580%25A7-%25E7%2595%25B6%25E5%259C%25B0%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E9%2580%259A%25E5%2581%259C%25E9%25A7%259B-%25E5%2585%25A8%25E5%25B8%2582%25E5%25B1%2585%25E5%25AE%25B6-7-%25E6%2597%25A5%2F&h=1869bfb1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/china/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A